rComments: Perfect Professor. An amazing lecturer, his voice is so melodious. He brings the material to life. Gives such clarity on how to do well on essays and exams. He really helps you! Performed live for the class with his band. Wish I could take this class again!!

The work you put in translates to your mark. He jumps around in his lectures a bit, so make sure you pay attention in class-otherwise, you're good. Very friendly and fairly helpful if you ask him questions. Rely on his lectures more than textbook for the exams unless you don't understand something.
